Logitech has launched its Circle 2 security camera, an indoor or outdoor unit which “can be placed anywhere”. The company said the Circle 2 is an evolution of the original Circle camera, and features various mounts and accessories, and a new mobile app for iOS and Android. “Two models are available, Wired and Wire-Free, which give you the freedom to position the Circle 2 camera wherever you want,” said Logitech. Mounts and accessories for the camera include: The camera features 1080p streaming, a 180-degree wide-angle lens, and two-way talk and listen. “Every Circle 2 camera comes with 24-hours of free, secure bank-level encrypted cloud storage,” said Logitech, with more storage options available. Pre-order pricing is as follows: 